Short      a Caverndeep Trogg~
Long       A Caverndeep Trogg snarls, clutching a jagged stone axe.
~
Desc       The troggs of Gnomeregan are larger and more aggressive than their surface
cousins, mutated by exposure to the city's radiation. Their gray skin has
taken on a sickly green tinge, and they attack with savage ferocity. They
have claimed entire sections of the lower city.
~
