Short      Mekgineer Thermaplugg~
Long       Mekgineer Thermaplugg sits in his battle suit, mad eyes gleaming.
~
Desc       The traitor who doomed Gnomeregan, Sicco Thermaplugg was once the city's
chief advisor. His jealousy of High Tinker Mekkatorque drove him to
sabotage the city's defenses and release radiation that killed thousands.
Now he rules from his battle suit, surrounded by bombs and mechanical
minions, utterly insane but terrifyingly intelligent.
~
