#ROOM
Vnum     14500
Name     &MDun Morogh - Gnomeregan Entrance&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     A massive metal door is set into the mountainside, bearing the cog-and-wrench
emblem of &MGnomeregan&d. Warning signs in multiple languages advise against
entry—the city has been declared a hazardous zone since its fall. Sickly
green light seeps from cracks around the door, and the faint hum of
machinery echoes from within. Dun Morogh lies to the &Yeast&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14710
Desc      The road leads back to Dun Morogh.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14714 2 14500
  Reset E 1 14716 1 16
  Reset E 1 14717 1 12
  Reset O 0 14526 1 14500 
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14501
Name     &MNew Tinker Town - Entry Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You step into the outermost section of Gnomeregan, now called &MNew Tinker
Town&d by the survivors who have established a foothold here. The air is
cleaner than deeper in the city, filtered by hastily constructed purifiers.
Gnome refugees huddle around makeshift shelters, and guards watch the
passages leading deeper with wary eyes. The exit lies &Yeast&d, and the
settlement continues &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14500
Desc      The entrance to Dun Morogh lies outside.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14502
Desc      New Tinker Town continues deeper.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14517 3 14501
Reset M 0 14518 1 14501
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14502
Name     &MNew Tinker Town - Refugee Camp&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Tents and lean-tos constructed from salvaged materials fill this chamber.
Gnome survivors have made this their home, refusing to abandon their city
entirely. A medical station has been set up to the &Ynorth&d, and an
engineering workshop lies to the &Ysouth&d. The entry chamber is &Yeast&d,
and a barricade blocks passage &Ywest&d into the dangerous deeper levels.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14503
Desc      The medical station lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14501
Desc      The entry chamber lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14504
Desc      The workshop lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14505
Desc      A barricade guards the passage west.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14517 5 14502
Reset M 0 14520 2 14502
Reset O 0 14519 5 14502
Reset O 0 14520 5 14502
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14503
Name     &MNew Tinker Town - Medical Station&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    nomob indoors~
Desc     Cots line the walls of this makeshift hospital, many occupied by gnomes
suffering from radiation sickness or injuries sustained in the fall of
the city. Medical equipment salvaged from deeper levels hums and beeps.
The air smells of antiseptic and desperation. A dedicated medic works
tirelessly to help those who can still be saved.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14502
Desc      The refugee camp lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14519 1 14503
Reset O 0 14520 3 14503
Reset O 0 14519 3 14503
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14504
Name     &MNew Tinker Town - Salvage Workshop&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The clatter of tools and hum of machinery fill this workshop, where
gnome engineers work to repair equipment and construct defenses. Salvaged
parts are sorted into bins, and half-finished projects cover every
workbench. Despite the dire circumstances, the gnomes maintain their
love of invention.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14502
Desc      The refugee camp lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14518 1 14504
Reset M 0 14517 2 14504
Reset O 0 14515 5 14504
Reset O 0 14516 5 14504
Reset O 0 14517 2 14504
Reset O 0 14523 1 14504
