#ROOM
Vnum     14505
Name     &MNew Tinker Town - Western Barricade&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A heavy barricade of welded metal and overturned machinery blocks the
passage leading deeper into Gnomeregan. Guards watch nervously through
viewing slits, ready for any leper gnomes or worse that might try to
break through. Warning signs declare the area beyond extremely hazardous.
The refugee camp lies &Yeast&d, and beyond the barricade lies the
&RHall of Gears&d to the &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14502
Desc      The refugee camp lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14510
Desc      The Hall of Gears lies beyond the barricade.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14517 2 14505
Reset O 0 14522 1 14505
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14510
Name     &xThe Hall of Gears - East Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     Beyond the safety of New Tinker Town, the true horror of &RGnomeregan&d
becomes apparent. The air is thick with radiation, and sickly green light
emanates from cracks in the walls. Massive gears—once the pride of gnomish
engineering—grind and screech overhead, many running erratically or jammed
with debris. The barricade lies &Yeast&d, and the hall continues &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14505
Desc      The barricade to New Tinker Town lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14511
Desc      The Hall of Gears continues west.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14500 3 14510
Reset M 0 14523 3 14510
Reset M 0 14520 1 14510
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14511
Name     &xThe Hall of Gears - Central Section&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     Enormous gears mesh overhead, their rhythmic grinding a constant reminder
that Gnomeregan's machinery continues to function even without sane hands
to guide it. Catwalks crisscross above the main floor, and ladders lead
to maintenance platforms. Leper gnomes scuttle in the shadows, driven mad
but still drawn to the machines they once tended. The hall continues &Yeast&d
and &Ywest&d, with passages branching &Ynorth&d and &Ysouth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14512
Desc      A passage leads north to the dormitory wing.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14510
Desc      The hall continues east.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14520
Desc      A passage leads south to the engineering labs.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14513
Desc      The hall continues west.
~
#ENDEXIT

