#ROOM
Vnum     14512
Name     &xDormitory Wing - South Corridor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This corridor once led to comfortable living quarters for Gnomeregan's
citizens. Now the walls are stained with radiation burns and splattered
with... other things. Doors hang open on empty rooms, and personal
belongings are scattered everywhere, abandoned in the panic of evacuation.
The Hall of Gears lies &Ysouth&d, and the corridor continues &Ynorth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14514
Desc      The corridor continues north.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14511
Desc      The Hall of Gears lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14500 3 14512
Reset M 0 14524 4 14512
Reset O 0 14517 1 14512
