#ROOM
Vnum     14513
Name     &xThe Hall of Gears - West Section&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The western section of the Hall of Gears shows more damage than the rest.
Several massive gears have stopped entirely, jammed by debris or sabotage.
Pools of toxic sludge have accumulated in low areas, glowing an ominous
green. The hall continues &Yeast&d, and a heavily reinforced door leads
&Ywest&d to the deeper levels. A ramp descends &Ydown&d to the Trogg tunnels.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14511
Desc      The hall continues east.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14530
Desc      A reinforced door leads to the deeper levels.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    14540
Desc      A ramp descends into the Trogg-infested tunnels.
~
#ENDEXIT

