#ROOM
Vnum     14514
Name     &xDormitory Wing - Central Hub&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     A circular hub connects the various dormitory sections. A dry fountain
sits in the center, its mechanical fish long since stopped moving. Doorways
lead to different housing blocks in all directions. Graffiti in gnomish
covers the walls—warnings, farewells, and the mad ravings of leper gnomes.
The corridor continues &Ysouth&d, and passages lead &Yeast&d, &Ywest&d, and
&Ynorth&d to different dormitory sections.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14515
Desc      A passage leads to the northern dormitories.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14516
Desc      A passage leads to the eastern dormitories.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14512
Desc      The corridor leads back south.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14517
Desc      A passage leads to the western dormitories.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14500 3 14514
Reset M 0 14520 2 14514
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14515
Name     &xDormitory Wing - North Block&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This dormitory block housed many of Gnomeregan's families. Small apartments
open onto the corridor, their doors mostly smashed or hanging open. Toys
and family portraits lie amid the debris—heartbreaking reminders of the
lives destroyed by Thermaplugg's treachery. Leper gnomes have made nests
in some of the rooms.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14514
Desc      The central hub lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT

