#ROOM
Vnum     14516
Name     &xDormitory Wing - East Block&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The eastern dormitories housed junior engineers and apprentices. Small
workbenches are built into many of the rooms, and half-finished projects
still sit where their creators left them. The radiation is particularly
strong here—a ruptured pipe in the ceiling leaks contaminated coolant.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14514
Desc      The central hub lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT

