Vnum     14517
Name     &xDormitory Wing - West Block&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     Senior engineers and officials lived in this block, evidenced by the
larger apartments and finer furnishings—now all destroyed or looted.
A leper gnome technician has set up a disturbing "workshop" in one room,
filled with dismembered mechanical parts and worse.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14514
Desc      The central hub lies to the east.
~
