Vnum     14520
Name     &xEngineering Labs - North Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     These laboratories were once the cutting edge of gnomish innovation.
Experimental devices line the walls, many still powered and humming
ominously. The radiation has caused some to malfunction in dangerous
ways—arcs of electricity and jets of steam erupt randomly. The Hall
of Gears lies &Ynorth&d, and the labs continue &Ysouth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14511
Desc      The Hall of Gears lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
