#ROOM
Vnum     14521
Name     &xEngineering Labs - Central Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The main laboratory chamber is a disaster zone. Equipment has been
overturned, and chemical spills cover the floor. Irradiated slimes have
spawned in the toxic pools, feeding on the contaminated materials. A
massive experiment in the center of the room has fused into something
unrecognizable and vaguely threatening.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14520
Desc      The labs continue to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14522
