#ROOM
Vnum     14522
Name     &xEngineering Labs - Weapons Research&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This lab was dedicated to weapons development—a necessary evil given
the threats facing Gnomeregan. Prototype blasters, explosives, and
defensive devices fill the shelves, many in various states of assembly.
Some have been taken by leper gnomes, making them even more dangerous.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14521
Desc      The central lab lies to the west.
~
