Vnum     14523
Name     &xEngineering Labs - South Section&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The southern labs specialized in robotics and automation. Workbenches
hold partially assembled constructs, and schematics for mechanical
servants cover the walls. Some of the constructs have activated on their
own, patrolling the area with corrupted programming.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14521
Desc      The central lab lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
