#ROOM
Vnum     14524
Name     &xEngineering Labs - Supply Storage&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This room stored components and materials for the laboratories. Most
has been looted or destroyed, but some supplies remain, scattered among
the debris. Shelving units have toppled, creating a maze of metal and
salvage.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14521
Desc      The central lab lies to the east.
~
