#ROOM
Vnum     14525
Name     &xEngineering Labs - Clean Room&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The irony is painful—this was once a hermetically sealed clean room for
delicate work. Now the seals have failed, and it is as contaminated as
everywhere else. The white walls are stained green, and the precision
equipment has been fouled beyond repair. An observation window overlooks
a deeper section of the complex.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14523
Desc      The labs continue to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14510 1 14525
Reset O 0 14525 2 14525
