#ROOM
Vnum     14530
Name     &RLaunch Bay - East Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The &RLaunch Bay&d was designed to deploy gnomish flying machines and
vehicles. The massive chamber stretches upward several stories, with
launch rails and catapults built into the walls. Most vehicles have
been destroyed or stolen, but a few damaged machines remain. Security
constructs patrol here with particular vigilance.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14513
Desc      The Hall of Gears lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14531
Desc      The bay continues to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT

