Vnum     14531
Name     &RLaunch Bay - Central Platform&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     A raised platform in the center of the bay served as the main launch
control center. Consoles are smashed or corrupted, but some still flicker
with power. A massive mechanical guardian stands watch over the area,
attacking anything that approaches. The bay continues &Yeast&d and &Ywest&d,
and a catwalk leads &Yup&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14530
Desc      The bay continues to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT

