Vnum     14532
Name     &RLaunch Bay - West Section&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The western section of the bay holds the remains of several flying
machines, crashed and burned during the chaos of the city's fall. Fuel
has leaked across the floor, making the area dangerously flammable.
A passage leads &Ysouth&d to &RTinkers' Court&d, the heart of Gnomeregan's
government.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14531
Desc      The bay continues to the east.
~
