Vnum     14533
Name     &RLaunch Bay - Upper Catwalk&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This catwalk runs along the upper walls of the Launch Bay, providing
access to the launch mechanisms and maintenance platforms. The view of
the devastation below is sobering. Alarm-O-Bots patrol this level,
watching for intruders.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    14531
Desc      The central platform lies below.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 14520 3 14533
Reset M 0 14521 1 14533
