#ROOM
Vnum     14540
Name     &xCaverndeep Tunnels - Upper Level&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     These tunnels were dug by Caverndeep troggs who broke through from below
during the city's fall. The walls are rough and unfinished, a stark
contrast to the smooth gnomish construction. Trogg totems and crude
drawings mark their territory. The ramp leads &Yup&d to the Hall of Gears,
and the tunnels continue &Ydown&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    14513
Desc      The ramp leads up to the Hall of Gears.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction down~
