Name     &xCaverndeep Tunnels - Middle Level&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The tunnels widen here into a series of chambers where the troggs have
established their main camp. Crude fire pits cast flickering shadows, and
the stench of the creatures is overwhelming. They have dragged salvaged
equipment down here, using it for incomprehensible purposes.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14543
Desc      A side tunnel leads east.
~
