#ROOM
Vnum     14542
Name     &xCaverndeep Tunnels - Lower Level&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The deepest level of the trogg tunnels is also the most dangerous.
&RGrubbis&d, the massive trogg leader, has claimed this area as his throne
room. The walls are decorated with trophies of his kills—gnome skulls,
mechanical parts, and worse. His loyal guards surround him constantly.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    14541
Desc      The tunnels lead back up.
~
