Name     &xCaverndeep Tunnels - Viscous Fallout's Lair&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This tunnel dead-ends in a pool of the most concentrated radioactive
waste in Gnomeregan. In this toxic soup dwells &RViscous Fallout&d, a
massive ooze creature that has achieved a horrible sentience. The glow
from its body is bright enough to illuminate the entire chamber.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14541
Desc      The tunnels lead back west.
