Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     &RTinkers' Court&d was the governmental heart of Gnomeregan, where the
High Tinker and the Council of Engineers administered the city. Now it
is a war zone, contested between security constructs, leper gnomes, and
worse. The ornate architecture is scarred by battle damage and radiation.
The Launch Bay lies &Ynorth&d, and the Court continues &Ysouth&d.
~
