Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The central forum was once a place of debate and innovation. A raised
platform held the High Tinker's seat, now empty. Screens that once
displayed engineering marvels are dark or show only static. &RElectrocutioner
6000&d patrols this area, devastating anything that moves with electrical
discharges.
~
