Desc     The heart of Gnomeregan's corruption, this chamber serves as &RMekgineer
Thermaplugg's&d throne room and workshop. Banks of monitors display views
throughout the city, and bomb dispensers line every wall. At the center,
Thermaplugg himself sits in a massive battle suit, surrounded by his most
dangerous creations. His eyes gleam with insane brilliance as he plots
the destruction of all who would challenge him.
